 # Changelog
 
+## Unreleased
+
+### Added
+- User profiles now support display_name, bio, free-text location with geocoding,
+  and a JSONB metadata bag for per-user preferences.
+- Mentions: `@handle` syntax in bios and other free-text fields creates a
+  Mention record and notifies the mentioned user via their preferred channel
+  (email / sms / webhook).
+- Admin endpoints: `/admin/users`, `/admin/users/search`, role grant + revoke,
+  audit event listing and CSV export, notification replay, and user
+  impersonation for support workflows.
+- AuditService records every administrative action with actor, target, and
+  payload for compliance.
+- ExportService produces full user-data exports (mentions, audit events,
+  sessions) for GDPR/DSR requests and uploads them to the export bucket.
+- FeedService assembles a home feed from mentions, follow activity, and
+  recent announcements.
+- NotificationService dispatches mentions and admin events across email,
+  sms, and signed webhooks with retry.
+
+### Changed
+- Roles now carry description, is_system, and created_at; system roles are
+  ensured at app startup.
+
